The generated report says the character is \"standing upright\" and \"not affected by the helicopter’s movement or wind,\" explicitly contradicting the oscillation, and it makes no mention of the non-spinning rotors or the unusual hovering behavior.  Because the generated report omits—and in one case conflicts with—the key abnormal behaviors that characterize the ground-truth issue, it cannot be considered the same underlying bug.","match":false}

No conflicting details suggest they refer to different issues.","match":true}
